-- Ken Martindale Promoted to Chief Operating Officer at Rite Aid Drug Chain
-- Stefanie Batcho-Lino
-- 2010-06-24T12:35:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-24/ken-martindale-promoted-to-chief-operating-officer-at-rite-aid-drug-chain.html

          
          
             Rite Aid Corp. said Ken Martindale
was promoted to chief operating officer from senior executive
vice president of merchandising, marketing and logistics. He
assumes the position from John Standley, who had been promoted
to chief executive officer.  
          
          


  


        